  "detailed_description": "Indie speed-run game with wall running, high octane gameplay, different weapons, enemies, explosions and much more,<br>Use your ability to control your movement and try finishing the round as soon as possible, also try to kill as many enemies as possible.<br><br>CONTROLS :<br>WASD - Movement.<br>Spacebar - Jump.<br>Spacebar[2x] - Double Jump.<br>Left Mouse Button - Fire.<br>Right Mouse Button[HOLD] - Ability.<br>Jump on a wall to - Enter wall run.<br>Jump from a wall to - Exit wall run.",
